{"type":"message","id":"b137541d","parentId":"d1b30e42","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:50:47.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n哦，本地是通的，服务状态是ok的，那用户打不开的话大概率是防火墙或者端口没有对外暴露的问题对吧？首先看一下防火墙规则，还有是不是服务只监听了localhost？不对刚才ss的结果是*:3102，也就是监听所有网卡对吧？那再检查ufw或者iptables的规则，看看3102端口有没有开放。首先执行ufw status看看防火墙状态，还有有没有开放3102端口。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c9f9kguu5igccslpdoi5nov4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ufw status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775793038639,"responseId":"0217757930378774bb2d320cfcd0d3dcaa0804120ace3f9f25a3f"}}
