{"type":"message","id":"fc2e9069","parentId":"36846a41","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:50:55.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n哦，那用户应该是在WSL里面？因为之前Runtime显示是WSL2对吧？WSL2的端口默认是不暴露给Windows主机或者外部网络的，需要做端口转发对吧？首先先确认一下WSL的IP地址，执行ip addr show eth0 | grep inet，拿到WSL的内部IP，然后告诉用户需要在Windows端做端口转发，或者检查是不是用户从外部访问而端口没映射？\n\n首先先查WSL的IP：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5wuu6vg9o9jfiudrcawftekg","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ip addr show eth0 | grep -oP '(?<=inet\\s)\\d+(\\.\\d+){3}'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775793050527,"responseId":"0217757930487394bb2d320cfcd0d3dcaa0804120ace3f9d52bb2"}}
