{"type":"message","id":"c4d70cdc","parentId":"2d0d1991","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:16:16.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n那我们刚才的问题是：修改了Gateway的端口为3102，但是现在3102还是被openclaw-router进程占用，所以Gateway没有成功绑定3102端口对吧？刚才我们curl 3102/health返回的是router的健康结果，不是Gateway的。Gateway现在是运行在3102吗？不对，刚才curl 3102/health返回的是{\"status\":\"ok\",\"uptime\":22...}，而Gateway的健康结果应该是{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}对吧？对哦，之前我们curl 3101/health的时候返回的是{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}，而3102现在返回的是router的结果，说明Gateway现在还是没能绑定3102端口，因为端口被占了。\n所以现在的问题是router进程被杀了之后会自动重启，我们得找到它的启动方式，先把它停掉，再重启Gateway。\n首先看一下这个router进程的父进程是谁？执行ps auxf | grep 23471 看看父进程。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_koxy0bbv7ugqpc70r71gcix3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps auxf | grep 23471"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775819769783,"responseId":"0217758197688248e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f4c6871f"}}
