{"type":"message","id":"a6152568","parentId":"79833b4a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:16:26.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n哦，父进程是1，也就是systemd，那说明这个router进程是被systemd管理的啊？但是刚才我们list-units的时候没看到？哦，可能是用户级别的systemd服务，或者是全局的？或者服务名不叫openclaw-router？我们再查一下所有的systemd服务，不管是不是用户的，看看有没有router相关的：systemctl list-unit-files | grep -i router。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_p02v8vbvxrxgi8q8hfvhzx7w","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"systemctl list-unit-files | grep -i router 2>/dev/null || echo \"no router service found in global systemd\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775819782306,"responseId":"0217758197822598e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f4dfaef6"}}
