{"type":"message","id":"28170dc0","parentId":"604d6b88","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:16:31.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n哦！原来openclaw-router.service是全局的systemd服务，不是用户级别的，所以刚才我们--user的list-units看不到。哦对，所以现在我们需要先停止这个全局的openclaw-router服务，然后再重启Gateway服务，这样3102端口就会被Gateway占用了。\n对吧？那现在执行命令：sudo systemctl stop openclaw-router.service && sudo systemctl disable openclaw-router.service，然后重启Gateway。\n不过等一下，执行sudo命令需要权限对吧？我们先试试。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_r4eqjgi1wwhc97h14aadlhf1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sudo systemctl stop openclaw-router.service && sudo systemctl disable openclaw-router.service && systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway.service && sleep 2 && curl http://localhost:3102/health"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775819787633,"responseId":"0217758197872688e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f48968be"}}
