{"type":"message","id":"524e767d","parentId":"56307c7e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:16:37.225Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n哦，需要sudo密码，我们没有权限执行sudo命令对吧？那得告诉用户这个情况：\n现在回退操作遇到权限问题，openclaw-router服务是全局systemd服务，需要sudo权限才能停止，我无法直接执行。\n请你手动执行以下命令完成回退：\n```bash\n# 停止并禁用路由代理服务\nsudo systemctl stop openclaw-router.service\nsudo systemctl disable openclaw-router.service\n\n# 重启Gateway服务\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway.service\n\n# 验证\ncurl http://localhost:3102/health\n```\n当返回 `{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}` 说明回退成功，Gateway已经接管3102端口。\n对吧？\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当前回退操作遇到权限限制：`openclaw-router` 是全局systemd服务，需要sudo权限才能停止，我无法直接执行。\n\n请你手动执行以下命令完成最后一步回退：\n```bash\n# 停止并禁用路由代理服务（需要输入密码）\nsudo systemctl stop openclaw-router.service\nsudo systemctl disable openclaw-router.service\n\n# 重启Gateway服务\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway.service\n\n# 验证结果\ncurl http://localhost:3102/health\n```\n当返回 `{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}` 说明回退成功，Gateway已成功接管3102端口，WebChat可正常访问。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775819791656,"responseId":"0217758197910488e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f42f6618"}}
